text: Bumetopia borneensis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1969. It is known from Borneo.BioLib.cz - Bumetopia borneensis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1969
title: Bumetopia borneensis
